xxl.core.relational.parser
Class CqlParser

java.lang.Object
  xxl.core.relational.parser.CqlParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
CqlParserConstants
public class CqlParser
extends Object
implements CqlParserConstants

This class provides a parser for CQL. The parser is defined by a JavaCC grammar which rules are shown in the documentation of the parser's methods.

Field Detail

tableFactory

protected Function<Node,Node> tableFactory
The table factory is internally used to map table references to logical constructs representing the tables of a relational database. By setting system-dependent table factories the CQL parser can be easily adapted to deal with different database implementations without changing the code of the parser.
